	Shoplift    
	 London, April 26 (PTI): Britain has emerged as one of the foremost countries where shoplifting is rampant, a study by the World Economic Forum has revealed.      
	 official league table of the worlds most crooked countries, prepared by the forum, has revealed that British businesses are more likely to be hit by thieves than almost anywhere else in the world. Stores in Britain report a crime to police every two minutes, the Daily Star reported.                                                                                                                                                                       
